    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in fair condition. The exterior has some scratches and minor dents, with paint that shows noticeable fading in areas but no significant rust. The interior has moderate wear on the upholstery and trim, and all major mechanical systems are functional, though some components may need attention in the near future. Overall, it is a serviceable vehicle suitable for everyday use.",
      "price": 20000.0,
